\begin{align}
\left|\psi\left(x\right)\right|^2 = N \sin\left(\frac{n\pi x}{L} \right) N \sin\left(\frac{n\pi x}{L} \right)\\
\left|\psi\left(x\right)\right|^2 = N^2 \sin^2\left(\frac{n\pi x}{L} \right)
